* {{audio|En-us-goodbye.ogg|Audio (US)}}
* {{rhymes|aɪ}}

===Interjection===
{{en-intj}}

# [[farewell]]; a formula used to another person or persons when the speaker or writer or the person addressed to is [[depart]]ing.

